ActFarm Products Agencies Act
SubjectFederal-Provincial-Territorial Agreement on Guiding Principles for the Marketing of Eggs in Canada
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food enters into the FEDERAL-PROVINCIAL-TERRITORIAL AGREEMENT ON GUIDING PRINCIPLES FOR THE MARKETING OF EGGS IN CANADA in order to outline the guiding principles for the marketing of eggs and provide a blueprint for egg industry operations in Canada.
AttachmentsAttachment
